.SH NAME
zellij-new \- Launch and manage Zellij sessions with predefined configurations

.SH DESCRIPTION
A comprehensive command-line tool for creating, managing, and launching Zellij sessions with predefined tab layouts and configurations. Provides session management, development environments, and leverages Zellij's built-in session serialization.

.SH SYNOPSIS
zellij-new [options] [command] [arguments...]

